        <!-- Lipoma Surgery Simulator -->
        <div class="row" style=" background-color: var(--secondary-color);">
            <div class="column">
                <!-- YouTube Frame -->
                <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Jc6QFovmRck?si=5Utht4aecYS4IzpE"
                    title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0"
                    allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                    allowfullscreen>
                </iframe>
            </div>
            <!-- Project Description -->
            <div class="column">
                <h1>Collaborative Surgery Simulator</h1>
                <br>
                <p>
                    Prototype of a multi-user environment simulator for lipoma extraction surgery,
                    with some of its features including:
                <ul>
                    <li> Online Multiplayer system where each user can choose a specific role (surgeon, assistant,
                        resident, etc) and chat through a voice chat feature.</li>
                    <li> Real time 3D mesh modification.</li>
                    <li> Avatars animations, both hand controls.</li>
                    <li> Object transfer between users.</li>
                </ul>
                <br>
                This project was featured at an IEEE conference. You can find it
                <a href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9419164" target="_blank" style="color: white;"> here.</a>
                </p>

            </div>
        </div>

        <!--UNO-->
        <div class="row" style="background-color: var(--main-color);">
            <!-- Project Description -->
            <div class="column">
                <h1>UNO 3D</h1>
                <br>
                <p>
                    Videogame of the popular card game UNO, but in a 3D immersive version:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li> Multiplayer system (up to 6 players).</li>
                    <li> Animations for special cards.</li>
                    <li> Complete game logic implemented.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="column">
                <!-- YouTube Frame -->
                <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HDGS-Jimu5M?si=d0NNyWFNcOJw1_4a"
